deque
Class NodeDeque<E>

java.lang.Object
  deque.NodeDeque<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the element type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Deque<E>
public class NodeDeque<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Deque<E>

The NodeDeque class implements deque interface with a double-linked list. When a deque is first created, it contains no items.

1.0
